## ✅ Subtask 1.2 Complete

**Summary:** Added `@keyframes toast-out` animation and `.animate-toast-out` CSS class to the Toast component.

### Changes Made
Added to `web/src/components/Toast.jsx`:

```css
@keyframes toast-out {
  0% {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
  }
  100% {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(-100%) scale(0.95);
  }
}
.animate-toast-out {
  animation: toast-out 0.3s ease-in forwards;
}
```

### Acceptance Criteria Verified
- ✅ `toast-out` keyframes defined with `translateY(-100%)` and `opacity 0`
- ✅ `animate-toast-out` class applies the exit animation
- ✅ Animation duration matches entrance animation (0.3s)

### Additional Design Decisions
- Used `ease-in` timing (vs `ease-out` for entrance) for more natural exit feel
- Added `forwards` fill-mode to retain the final animation state (keeps toast hidden)
- Animation mirrors the entrance animation for visual consistency

**Commit:** `8424e8a` - auto-claude: 1.2 - Add @keyframes for toast-out animation that slides up and fades out

